   Summary:

   Flux's comment system supports:
   ✓ Single-line comments (//)
   ✓ Block comments (/* */)
   ✓ Arbitrarily nested block comments
   ✓ Line doc comments (///)
   ✓ Block doc comments (/** */)
   ✓ Nested doc comments

   This makes it easy to comment out large code sections
   without worrying about breaking existing comments!
*/
